    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with several minor door dings, some paint fading on the hood, and a small crack in the rear bumper. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, though the suspension is starting to feel a bit loose and will likely need new struts in the near future. The interior is generally clean but does show visible wear on the driver's seat bolster and a few stains on the passenger carpet. It is a reliable transportation option that has been maintained regularly, even if it isn't aesthetically perfect.",
