    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my reliable ride that\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my daily commutes and weekend trips. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it still runs like a dream! It\u2019s perfect for someone looking for a great value without sacrificing quality. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 31500.0,
