    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound driver's car featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Engineered for precision, it benefits from a factory-spec limited-slip differential and upgraded Bilstein dampers for enhanced cornering flat-rate. The VANOS system has been recently serviced, and the rear subframe has been inspected for structural integrity. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with a well-loved performance vehicle, the powertrain remains robust with excellent compression and sharp throttle response from the individual throttle bodies. This is a visceral, analog machine ready for the canyon roads.",
